members.member:
            
                Submit Ticket
            
            
            /// 
            Role:  Authorize only

            Description:  Bind subjects and send selected subject RequestId. 

                    Bind availabe target roles using the provided Api ["BindTargetRolesForTicket"] (Available Target role for each user is 
                    based on he's role, e.g: user with role Customer can submit ticket for he's related Agent,
                    Vendor or contact admin via the ticket). 

                    If an agent submit a ticket to vendor, It will be bound to he's related vendor as well as the admin.

            Fields:
            {
                

"initialMessage": "Initial message to start ticket"


                        "targetRole": {
                        


                                "gcode": 5, The G-code representing the target role.
                            
                        
                    


                        "subject": {
                        


                                "id": 2, The ID of the selected subject.
                            
                        
                    
                
            }

